    <item>
      <title>新兴市场投资者为美国关税提供“身体打击”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/asia-currencies-stocks-lead-emerging-peers-lower-amid-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统宣布对出口驱动的国家的高关税之后，整个发展中国家的资产跌跌撞撞，最小，最弱的经济体针对中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/asia-currencies-stocks-lead-emerging-peers-lower-amid-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 06:44:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税显示后，印度资产比亚洲其他地区要好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/indian-assets-fare-better-than-asia-as-tariff-blow-seen-mild</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税措施对国家的经济增长和企业利润的严重程度之后，印度资产的遭受的损失少于亚洲同行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/indian-assets-fare-better-than-asia-as-tariff-blow-seen-mild</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 05:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国想要我们谈话，准备减少贸易盈余</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/thailand-pm-says-prepared-to-deal-with-us-tariffs-plans-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据总理佩顿顿·辛纳瓦特拉（Paetongtarn Shinawatra）称，泰国准备应对特朗普政府征收的36％互惠关税的后果，他表示该国准备采取措施在谈判后采取措施减少与美国的贸易盈余。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/thailand-pm-says-prepared-to-deal-with-us-tariffs-plans-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 03:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾认为，随着特朗普的关税更加努力，好处</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/philippine-exporters-may-raise-prices-after-us-tariffs-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员们说，菲律宾试图以美国相对于亚洲邻国的出口征收的较低关税兑现，并将努力改善其与长期盟友的经济联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/philippine-exporters-may-raise-prices-after-us-tariffs-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 02:32:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普关税威胁经济增长时，欧洲的股票下沉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/european-stock-futures-decline-as-trump-tariffs-hurt-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）宣布了一个世纪以来对贸易伙伴的最陡峭的美国关税之后，欧洲股票跌倒，其中包括欧盟的20％税率，欧盟正在考虑如何进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/european-stock-futures-decline-as-trump-tariffs-hurt-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:57:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票，美元水槽作为关税冲击回响：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者抛弃了股票，并逃离了国债的安全，因为唐纳德·特朗普总统竞标重塑世界贸易命令威胁着破坏经济增长。美元在两年半内最大的下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿巴巴眼睛迪拜办公室作为非洲繁荣的海湾资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/south-africa-bank-absa-to-open-dubai-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据资产计划，南非第三大银行的单位计划明年在迪拜开设代表办事处，以受益于中东和非洲之间不断增长的贸易和投资。]]></description>
